high_descs: Turn right, then left, then right again to reach the toilet.
Pick up the rightmost candle on the back of the toilet.
Go to the cabinet beneath the sink and to the right of the toilet.
Place the candle in the cabinet, behind the soap.
anns.task_desc: Put a candle in the cabinet.

high_descs: turn and walk over to the toilet
grab the right side candle off the top of the toilet
back up a bit to face the bathroom cabinet
place the candle inside of the bathroom cabinet
anns.task_desc: place a candle inside the bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Go across the room to the toilet.
Pick up the candlestick on the right.
Open the cabinet under the sink on the left side, put the candlestick in the cabinet, and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a candlestick in the cabinet under the sink.
